OL,3,C'Free' heating and post-work
OL,4,Cgatherings tempting workers back to
OL,5,Coffice ` index
OL,7,FTwo-thirds (67%) of people say "free"
OL,8,Fheating encourages them to venture
OL,9,Finto the office during the chilly
OL,10,Fwinter months, according to an index.
OL,12,FNearly half (48%) of workers now
OL,13,Fcommute to their workplace five days a
OL,14,Fweek, according to the Virgin Media O2
OL,15,FBusiness Movers Index.
OL,17,FNine in 10 (90%) workers have signed
OL,18,Fup to at least one loyalty programme,
OL,19,Fwith meal deals and coffee deals being
OL,20,Fthe most used.
