OL,7,FThe quarterly index combines
OL,8,Fanonymised and aggregated UK movement
OL,9,Fdata from O2 Motion with survey
OL,10,Ffindings.
OL,12,FO2 Motion has been created by the
OL,13,Fmobile phone network to offer insight
OL,14,Finto movement trends across the UK.
OL,16,FAs mobile devices connect to different
OL,17,Fmasts, they create data "footprints"
OL,18,Fwhich O2 can anonymise and aggregate
OL,19,Fto gain a picture of how people are
OL,20,Ftravelling, when they make journeys
OL,21,Fand which areas they visit.
