OL,7,FO2 Motion does not capture
OL,8,Finternational visitors in the UK or
OL,9,Fchildren and does not collect GPS data.
OL,11,FThe research indicated that Monday and
OL,12,FFriday commutes have seen 7% and 5%
OL,13,Fyear-on-year increases respectively.
OL,15,FMobile data also indicates a rising
OL,16,Ftrend in younger workers aged 18 to 24
OL,17,Fstaying out after work, with an
OL,18,Fincrease in after-work trips.
