OL,7,FThe research also indicates that
OL,8,Fshopping centre visits have increased
OL,9,Ffor people aged 55 to 64 and those 65-
OL,10,Fplus.
OL,12,FNearly one in four (24%) people plan
OL,13,Fto start holiday shopping earlier this
OL,14,Fyear, with a third (34%) intending to
OL,15,Fbuy more affordable gifts, and 32%
OL,16,Fexpecting to take advantage of Black
OL,17,FFriday deals.
OL,19,FSome of 2,000 people were surveyed
OL,20,Facross the UK in October as part of
OL,21,Fthe latest research.
