OL,7,FJo Bertram, managing director of
OL,8,FVirgin Media O2 Business, said the
OL,9,Findex "shines a light on the positive
OL,10,Fimpact that people returning to the
OL,11,Foffice can make to retailers.
OL,13,F"Whether it's creating eye-catching
OL,14,Fseasonal campaigns in shops near busy
OL,15,Foffice locations or making sure
OL,16,Fcustomers have the best possible in-
OL,17,Fstore experience, retailers have a
OL,18,Fsignificant opportunity to get
OL,19,Fcreative when it comes to engaging
OL,20,Fprospective customers."
